quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,28,"Humitu…ďe wonnde ndiyam woyndu ma…ď…ďe ndun, ko senndaa…óam hakkunde e ma…ď…ďe e ngelooba mbam: mba yara √Īallal, …ďe yara √Īallal. Kala ma…ď…ďe yara ge…ďal mun ka√Īum tun, e √Īalaande mun nden."
  54,29,"∆Āe noddiri wonndii…óo ma…ď…ďe on, fii warugol mba. O jonni kaafa kan, o wari mba e yamaruyee yim…ďe makko …ďen."
  54,30,"Taskee onon yim…ďe Makka …ďen, ko honno lepte Am …óen wa'unoo e ma…ď…ďe? Tasko…óon kadi ko honno Mi jertinirnoo …óum e wo…ó…ďe goo?"
  54,31,"Ko haacaango wooturu tun Men wurtunoo e ma…ď…ďe, ngo halki …ďe, …ďe wa'i le…ó…óe caŇče yooru…óe …óe gaynaako wallitorta dammi mun."
  54,32,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tasakuyeeji mayre."
  54,33,"Yum…ďe Luutu …ďen fennuno waaju Nulaa…óo ma…ď…ďe on Luutu (yo o his)."
  54,34,"Men wurtuno henndu kaa∆īe e ma…ď…ďe, si wanaa e …ďeynguure Luutu nden (yo o his) lepte …óen hewtaano …ďe, tawde Men da…ónuno …ďe fewndo o yaltidunoo e ma…ď…ďe ka wenndoogo, ado lepte …óen yanude e …ďeya."
  54,35,"Men da…óniri …ďe lepte …óen, mo∆ī∆īere Amen e ma…ď…ďe. Ko wano Men yo…ďitiri non Luutu, Men yo…ďitirta kala yettu…óo neema Allah on e makko."
  54,36,"Gom…óii le Luutu hul…ďinirno …ďe lepte Amen …óen. Kono …ďe yeddondiri e jertinol makko gol, …ďe fenni mo."
  54,37,"Gom…óii …ďe …óa…ď…ďirno Luutu accidugol …ďe e ho…ó…ďe makko …ďen, fii no …ďe huuwira paŇčnkare e ma…ď…ďe. Laatii Men mahi gite ma…ď…ďe …óen, …ďe acci yi'ude, …ďe wi'ani …ďe: mee…óee non lepte …óen e bone salagol jertinol Am ngol."
  54,38,"Gom…óii lepte duumii…óe dawiranno …ďe bimmbi law, ko heddoda e ma…ď…ďe haa laakara, lepte …óen ton kadi he…ďa …ďe."
  54,39,"∆Āe wi'aee ontuma: Mee…óee lepte Am …óe Mi li…ďi e mon …óen, e salagol mon jertiaango Luutu ngol."
  54,40,"Gom…óii Men newinirii Alquur'aanaare nden waajitorgol. Hara no woodi waajitoray…óo tesakuyeeji mayre."
  54,41,"Gom…óii jertinaango Amen ngon arii e yim…ďe Fir'awna …ďen, e dow …óemngal Muusaa e Haaruuna, yo …ďe his."
  54,42,"∆Āe fenni kala hujja e …ďanngannduyeeji immor…ói e Amen. Men yagginiri …ďe fennugol …ďe ngol, lepte Foolu…óo Mo fooletaake, Hattan…óo Mo ronkataa hay huunde."
  54,43,"Kere ko heefer…ďe mon …ďen onon yim…ďe Makkah …ďen, …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude e dii …ďeya heefer…ďe jantaa…ďe (Yim…ďe Nuuhu, e Aadi'en, e Samuuda'en, e Yim…ďe Luutu …ďen e Fir'awna e yim…ďe mun?) Kaa ko da…óugol e lepte Allah …óen woni maandinanaa on e Defte jippii…óe …óen?"
  54,44,"Kaa hara …ďee heefer…ďe Maakkah wi'ay: menen ko men dental wallindiroo…ďe e hoore kala faandanii…óo men bone, e…ď…ďu…óo senndugol men?"
  54,45,"Aray nden dental …ďee heefer…ďe foolee, …ďe huccintina …ďabbe, yeeso gom…óim…ďe …ďen. ∆äum wa…óuno √Īalnde hare nde Badri."
  54,46,"Wurin ko Darngal ngal …ďe fennunoo ngal, woni fodoore leptugol …ďe ngol. Ko Darngal non …ďuri mawnude e sa…ótude lepte dii ko …ďe leptanoo kon aduna ka Badri."
  54,47,"pellet, bonnir…ďe geddi e keeferaaku …ďen, wonii e majjere wo…ó…óiinde goonga, e lepte e tampere kadi."
  54,48,"√Ďalnde …ďe daasiroytee geece ma…ď…ďe …óen ka nder Yiite, …ďe wi'anee : mee…óee non lepte Yiite ngen."
  54,49,"Men tagir huunde kala e e…ď…ďoore Amen yawtunde, tippude e anndal e muy…óe Amen, wonndude e ko Men winndunoo ka Alluwal reenaangal."